Call for Papers

The Kernelcon Crew is soliciting presentations for the fourth annual Kernelcon held at the Downtown Embassy Suites in Omaha, NE, April 1-2, 2022.

Conclude novel research? Create something fun in your home lab? Develop a new technique? Wish you could spare someone else the horrors you faced? Impart your wisdom, start the conversations that need to be started, submit your work to our CFP!

As you plan your submission, feel free to peruse the{" "} 2019 program {" "} or the{" "} 2020 program {" "} .
